            (in the future) manage roles and channels. Just say "sans car" anywhere in a server or "sans help" for a list of
            commands.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="call-to-action">
        <!-- TODO: Make this from a model. (no hardcoding) -->
        <a href="https://sanscar.net/add-bot">
            <button class="add-sans-car-button">Add sans to your server</button>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="features-container">
    <div>
        <h1>Quotes</h1>
        <p>This is some placeholder text that will talk about how sans can manage your quotes.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h1>Audio</h1>
        <p>This is some placeholder text that will talk about how sans can play and queue audio for you and your friends.</p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="contact-container">
    <h1>Contribute</h1>
    <p>Sans car is open source on GitHub. If you have any issues, feel free to submit a pull request.</p>
</div>
</body>
